node.text:
As part of their campaign to plant 1 million trees a year, Endura agreed to plant an extra 100 trees for every second I can keep my back wheel in the air! Gave it my best shot and my arms are still feeling it! Big up to @enduraofficial for their journey to become carbon neutral by 2024! 
#endura

node.text:
Excited to show you guys my new mtb discipline 😉 “HIGHLAND WARRIOR TM” . It’s a mix of extreme enduro and Speed Trials all mashed together on a sketchy wee course in the garden haha!  Would love to see some courses you guys build your selves, please tag them with the hashtag #highlandwarrior !! Look forward to seeing what you all come up with! 
Filmed by @sempley_rory on my @gopro Hero8
#highlandwarrior #speedtrials #extremeenduro #fun

node.title: HIGHLAND WARRIOR  EXTREME ENDURO SPEED TRIALS OBSTACLE COURSE
